data.description:
This spacious two-story home is an inviting haven for families and entertainers alike, offering 6 bedrooms and 3 full baths. From the moment you enter, you'll be captivated by the open and airy design that seamlessly combines comfort and style. 
The ground floor features a separate bedroom, ideal for guests, a home office, or in-laws. The spacious kitchen opens to the living room and sunroom, creating a gourmet paradise with abundant counter space, stainless steel appliances, and a large walk-in pantry. 
On the second floor, you’ll discover spacious bedrooms and an extra large primary suite that features ample space and his and her closets.
This home has been thoroughly updated with fresh paint, new carpets, new light fixtures, stainless appliances, refinished hardwoods, new faucets, vanity countertops and more.  
Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a 6-bedroom home in the Wesley Chapel section of Monroe.
